  <description value="Bulk Member Match Operation enables Payers to match multiple members against another Payer's records for bulk data exchange. The operation returns Group resources containing matched, non-matched, and constrained members. The matched members Group can be used with the $davinci-data-export operation to retrieve bulk FHIR data for all matched members. The $davinci-data-export operation returns a manifest file referencing bulk data files in ndjson format."/>
